{"html": [{"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&#xA0;</div></div>", "i": 8305045}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Por Resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xBA; 1.052, de 18 de julio de 1997, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a de Pesca, del Ministerio de Econom&#xED;a, Fomento y Reconstrucci&#xF3;n, modif&#xED;case el numeral 1&#xBA; de la Resoluci&#xF3;n N&#xBA; 407, de 1995, de esta Subsecretar&#xED;a, que autoriz&#xF3; a PESQUERA EL GOLFO S.A., para sustituir diversas naves de la interesada por la nave &quot;Bronco&quot;, en el sentido de actualizar las caracter&#xED;sticas n&#xE1;uticas de esta &#xFA;ltima, en los t&#xE9;rminos que se indica:</div><br><br><div class=\"p\">Nombre&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &quot;Bronco&quot;</div><div class=\"p\">Matr&#xED;cula&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 2856</div><div class=\"p\">Eslora de arqueo&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  51,4&nbsp; &nbsp; m.</div><div class=\"p\">T.R.G. (Nacional)&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 886&nbsp; &nbsp;  t.</div><div class=\"p\">Capacidad de bodega&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 1148,6&nbsp; m3</div><div class=\"p\">Arte de pesca&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; Cerco.</div><br></div>", "i": 8305046}, {"t": "<div><div class=\"p\">&nbsp; &nbsp;  Valpara&#xED;so, 18 de julio de 1997.- Juan Manuel Cruz S&#xE1;nchez, Subsecretario de Pesca.</div><br></div>", "i": 8305047}], "proyectos": [], "otrosSistemas": [], "jurisprudencia": [], "doctrina": [], "metadatos": {"tiene_notas": false, "tipos_numeros": [{"tipo": "3", "nu